README OPENNMS MONITORING SOLUTION

This file will go into the details for deploying and managing the opennms monitoring solution.

The following modifications need to be done:

Place 'monitor' and 'onmsmon.php' into /opt/opennms

Place 'onmsmon' into /etc/init.d

Replace 'opennms' in /etc/init.d with included 'opennms' file

Make sure that all instances of onmsmon.php that are currently running are closed.

Do /etc/init.d/onmsmon start

Done!


